{"tid":2220852,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"明知道阿仙奴反勝利物浦不可能會，我還傻傻等到奇蹟出現的那一天","createTime":"2020-09-28T03:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T20:39:19.000Z","uid":38189,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dccf9e31b15fcfd0312c11bbed47249807c62850","tid":2220852,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T03:19:20.000Z","msg":"想用一張紅牌把你帶走　好讓我能容易踢一點<br />\n輸波的滋味　利不懂這種感覺　早拿英超的利永遠不會<br />\n<br />\n看見法賓奴在我面前　證明拉卡錫只是愚昧<br />\n利不懂我的　垃圾後防　是利永遠不曾過的體會<br />\n<br />\n為你(韋利)射出那種單刀你永遠救到晒<br />\n我又何苦勉強自己深夜睇場西波<br />\n利迷狠狠逼退　我的防備<br />\n達sir關上門來默數我的淚<br />\n<br />\n明知道阿仙奴反勝利物浦不可能會<br />\n我還傻傻等到奇蹟出現的那一天<br />\n重奪那一天　你會發現<br />\n真正愛您的雲加獨自守著傷悲"},{"pid":"1eda4d017db6da3d19ad16996427bce5fa2892aa","tid":2220852,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T03:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d7bcb2d4bf34a3d6c18cddc3ab680757384262","tid":2220852,"uid":222390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T03:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e7e4a019009850c455c79897a7a037562ff646","tid":2220852,"uid":72497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T03:21:13.000Z","msg":"為你(韋利)）（毁痢）"},{"pid":"78222a9bdaec63f75d6fefe57d5cdb0525da9e69","tid":2220852,"uid":222390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"好高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc649e78b8b5374b38250caeefd1f900cb46461","tid":2220852,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T03:22:03.000Z","msg":"雲加老師同圣杰老師=球壇樂壇雙巨頭"},{"pid":"b2930867271e17b8d0d242df0554e2d41305a8fa","tid":2220852,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T03:22:34.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">為你(韋利)</span><br />\n語帶雙關 撚打林多 屈到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ad